B.Mz=new A.K(B.a8,"Why technical vocabulary matters",'Aviation exams test your ability to understand and use precise technical terms. A technician saying "the thing that lifts the plane" instead of "the **aileron**" is unprofessional and dangerous.\n\nThis lesson covers the most frequently tested components grouped by aircraft system.',null,null,null)
B.NN=new A.K(B.B,"\ud83d\udee9\ufe0f Flight Control Surfaces","**Ailerons** \u2014 on the wings; control roll (bank left/right)\n**Elevator** \u2014 on the horizontal stabilizer; controls pitch (nose up/down)\n**Rudder** \u2014 on the vertical stabilizer; controls yaw (nose left/right)\n**Flaps** \u2014 on wing trailing edge; increase lift and drag during takeoff/landing\n**Spoilers** \u2014 on wings; reduce lift, increase drag, assist in roll control",null,null,null)
B.MC=new A.K(B.B,"\u2699\ufe0f Powerplant & Fuel Systems","**Turbine engine** \u2014 compressor \u2192 combustion chamber \u2192 turbine \u2192 nozzle\n**HP fuel shutoff valve** \u2014 high-pressure fuel control valve\n**Fuel manifold** \u2014 distributes fuel to combustion chambers\n**Gearbox** \u2014 transfers power between engine components\n**Nacelle** \u2014 streamlined housing enclosing the engine",null,null,null)
B.OV=new A.K(B.B,"\ud83d\udd27 Hydraulic & Landing Gear","**Hydraulic actuator** \u2014 converts hydraulic pressure to mechanical movement\n**Hydraulic pump** \u2014 pressurizes hydraulic fluid\n**Landing gear strut** \u2014 shock-absorbing leg of landing gear\n**Torque link** \u2014 scissors linkage preventing wheel rotation on strut\n**Brake assembly** \u2014 disc brakes on main landing gear wheels",null,null,null)
B.Iz=new A.az("The ailerons deflect differentially to produce a rolling moment.","Eleronlar, yuvarlanma momenti \xfcretmek i\xe7in farkl\u0131 a\xe7\u0131larda sapma yapar.","ailerons")
B.J2=new A.az(u.d,"Hidrolik pompa, motor taraf\u0131ndan di\u015fli kutusu arac\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131yla tahrik edilir.","hydraulic pump")
B.Iu=new A.az("Flap extension increases the camber of the wing and generates additional lift.","Flap a\xe7\u0131l\u0131m\u0131 kanat kavisini art\u0131r\u0131r ve ilave kald\u0131rma kuvveti \xfcretir.","Flap extension")
B.S2=s([B.Iz,B.J2,B.Iu],t.l)
B.P2=new A.K(B.a9,"In-Context Examples",null,B.S2,null,null)
B.OM=new A.K(B.aa,"\u2708\ufe0f Exam Tip",'Vocabulary questions often ask for **synonyms**. Common traps:\n\u2022 "nacelle" \u2260 "fuselage" (nacelle is the engine housing)\n\u2022 "aileron" controls **roll**, not yaw\n\u2022 "elevator" controls **pitch**, not roll\n\nMemory trick: **A**ileron \u2192 **A**xis of roll, **E**levator \u2192 **E**levation (pitch), **R**udder \u2192 **R**otation around yaw axis.',null,null,null)
