B.UL=s(["In accordance with SOPs","Violating or not following SOPs","Similar to SOPs in other companies","An improvement over SOPs"],t.s)
B.a0f=new A.a5(-301,B.b2,461,'"Contrary to standard operating procedures" means:',B.UL,1,B.z,null,null,null)
B.UE=s(["The main cause was crew rest","Crew rest was one element that made the accident more likely","Crew rest alone caused the accident","The crew rested adequately"],t.s)
